snippet.title: Closets: Tasya van Ree
snippet.description:
http://stylelikeu.com/

Elisa & Lily, the mother-daughters founders behind StyleLikeU, interview LA photographer and painter Tasya van Ree. Find out about Tasya's personal style, the inspiration behind her art, her first experience with heartbreak, and more. For more Tasya: http://stylelik.eu/17vaTdt.


YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/user/stylelikeu
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/stylelikeu
Twitter: https://twitter.com/StyleLikeU
Tumblr: http://stylelikeu.tumblr.com/
Instagram: http://instagram.com/stylelikeu#

Buy Our New Book, True Style Is What's Underneath: The Self-Acceptance Revolution: https://www.amazon.com/True-Style-Whats-Underneath-Self-Acceptance/dp/0789332868?_encoding=UTF8&psc=1
